# Repository Entrypoint

- Start from `AGENTS.md`, not from ad-hoc assumptions.
- Use `docs/agent-context/` as the single source of truth for task shape, risk, architecture, and definition of done.
- Keep explanations to humans in Chinese when practical.
- Treat the existing Harness pages as an observation/debug surface, not the main coding workflow.
